                        <interp inst="t18680817-name-382" type="surname" value="BARHAM"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18680817-name-382" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES BARHAM</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a constable at Billingsgate Market—I saw the prisoner about 12.35, and heard a cry of "Stop thief"—I saw him in the hands of a constable, and saw him drop the watch on the pavement—I took charge of him until 731 <hi rend="italic">City</hi> came up.</p>
